<p class="">These 1 in 4 cookies (representing the 1 in 4 people who will experience a mental health issue in their lives), were donated by a wonderful woman named Angela for the shop we popped up in Pittsburgh to celebrate the opening of "Mindful," a six month exhibit at the Society for Contemporary Craft. &nbsp;She had been following our Facebook page, and contacted us about contributing to the shop. &nbsp;In addition to these cookies she created the logo cookies that adorn the front page of this site. &nbsp;</p>



































  

    
  
    

      

      
